org.hps.readout.util.collection

Class LCIOData<T,E extends LCIOCollection<T>,V extends Collection<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.readout.util.collection.LCIOData<T,E,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - - The object type of the data stored by the collection.
    E - - The type of LCIO collection parameters object used by the data set.
    V - - The collection that actually stores the data.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ManagedLCIOData, TriggeredLCIOData

    public abstract class LCIOData<T,E extends LCIOCollection<T>,V extends Collection<?>>
extends Object
    Class LCIOData functions as a superclass to all the readout framework LCIO collection data set objects. It requires that they define LCIO collection parameters, and provide access to the data sets.
